ote":{"pid":"52e4c2a6ce08cd49d618d269966a1d78f0a7ca39","tid":1911131,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:46:51.000Z","msg":"隔離?邊有咁多位?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"同台灣一樣，即係叫你唔好黎<br />\n邊有人會專登去隔離"},{"pid":"3ac1d6e68756750b8a09d9f800d98eb1c0d5fc56","tid":1911131,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:21:39.000Z","msg":"遲好過冇<br />\n希望3月有改善"},{"pid":"9dce4937e89754730594776aa4c0438eb1fecc2f","tid":1911131,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:23:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71ed67583f179f8ed810d7794763052f13924f67","tid":1911131,"uid":263651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dce4937e89754730594776aa4c0438eb1fecc2f","tid":1911131,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:23:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:25:18.000Z","msg":"封香港澳門, 但應該冇封台灣"},{"pid":"391ae885cc669d5fff1ebd9ca0d0bb7eb240ecb4","tid":1911131,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:27:39.000Z","msg":"取消香港, 澳門, 韓國免簽待遇, 真係冇得去日本睇櫻花, D港女肯出嚟暴動未?"},{"pid":"09fecbc062af483340a8884ede675c70355f47de","tid":1911131,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:31:36.000Z","msg":"Bno又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7eb3cee2fa09a66ac025d0b70f3512e8652ed1b","tid":1911131,"uid":22243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:31:40.000Z","msg":"日本正討論禁止港澳免簽證安排，中韓旅客入境須隔離14日。<br />\n<br />\n日本《讀賣新聞》、《産經新聞》報道，為防止新型冠狀病毒傳播，日本計劃暫停港澳免簽。中國及韓國旅客入境後須於指定地點進行強制隔離14日，並停止發出簽證給中國及韓國人，表示不希望中國及韓國遊客到訪日本。航空方面，來自中、韓的航班，只可於成田和關西國際機場降落。預計相關措施將於今晚再公佈。"},{"pid":"e456a2465c1e0a37451201f4c782515f0d784e2e","tid":1911131,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:35:37.000Z","msg":"wow"},{"pid":"9278c48f2f0dfde94526d